Add new CSS rules to `src/app.css` for the search input wrapper, icons, visibility toggling, and spinner animation. Place these rules in the toolbar section, after the existing `.toolbar input[type='text']:focus` rule.

DOM structure being styled (built by app.ts in a later task):
```html
